Remote Monitoring System Remote monitoring system can be used for any kind of industry for monitoring machinery, energy meter, weather station data, water meter, PLC, can control PLC output, read PLC input or analog input value, SCADA system, etc&hellip;
As all customers requirement is different we can provide custom solution.
Specification :  Power Supply : 24VDC / 12VDC / 230V AC 2G / 4G Network modbus support MQTT, HTTP TCP/IP RS-485 / RS-232 Communication Support Ethernet Communication Support Inbuilt Digital Input / Digital Output, this is remove need of extra PLC
